#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Pengenalan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&gcompris; is a completely free educational software suite which contains "
#| "a wide range of activities."
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is a rich educational software suite which contains a wide range "
"of activities."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; adalah rangkaian perangkat lunak pendidikan gratis yang berisi "
"berbagai aktifitas. "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It offers various activities aimed at covering a variety of fields. The "
"topics include reading and typing, arithmetics, geography, sciences, and "
"other topics. It is meant to be used both at home and at school."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide a development platform for "
#| "educational activities."
msgid ""
"The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide playful activities but always "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"Tujuan dari &gcompris; adalah untuk menyediakan platform pengembangan untuk "
"kegiatan pendidikan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
#| "\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPL license</ulink>."
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 license</ulink>. All "
"the code, except the engine for analog electricity activity is under <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 license</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; adalah bagian dari proyek &kde; dan ditempatkan di bawah <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">lisensi GPL</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/"
#| "&Linux;, &BSD;, MacOSX, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with "
#| "support of <emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher is required. 32 bits "
#| "color depth mandatory"
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with support of "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; telah tersedia pada operasi sistem berikut ini: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &Windows;, Android. Itu memerlukan kartu 3D dengan dukungan "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> atau lebih tinggi. Dengan kedalaman warna 32 "
"bit"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Penginstalan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The software is delivered under several forms. Follow the process according "
"to your case."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak ini disampaikan dalam beberapa bentuk. Ikuti proses sesuai "
"dengan kasus kamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&GNU;/&Linux; : Use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
#| "distribution. You may have to install the package gcompris-sound-en to "
#| "have the English voices. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; "
#| "distribution, please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris; "
#| "in your &Linux; distribution."
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
"please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris;."
msgstr ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: Gunakan paket yang dibawakan oleh distribusi &GNU;/&Linux;mu. "
"Kamu mungkin harus menginstal paket gcompris-sound-id untuk mendapatkan "
"suara berbahasa Indonesia. Jika &gcompris; tidak dikemas pada distribusi "
"&Linux;mu, Silahkan hubungi mereka untuk meminta dimasukannya &gcompris; "
"pada distribusi &Linux;mu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&Windows;: Delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
#| "Microsoft Store."
msgid ""
"&Windows;: delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
"Microsoft Store."
msgstr ""
"&Windows;: Disebarkan menggunakan pemasang klasik &Windows; atau via "
"Microsoft Store."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "MacOSX : Delivered under a classic installer. This version requires an "
#| "activation code."
msgid "&macOS;: delivered under a classic installer."
msgstr ""
"MacOSX: Disebarkan menggunakan installer klasik. Pada versi ini membutuhkan "
"kode aktivasi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
