#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Antarmuka pengguna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
#| "controlled with a mouse, it cannot be used without a mouse or a pointing "
#| "system."
msgid ""
"The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
"controlled with a mouse. Keyboard navigation is also available on most of "
"the activities."
msgstr ""
"Antarmuka dirancang agar mudah digunakan untuk anak kecil. &gcompris; "
"dikendalikan dengan mouse, tidak bisa digunakan tanpa mouse atau sistem "
"penunjuk. "

