msgid ""
"Question mark — Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can be "
"too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this case, "
"this function gives access to additional information."
msgstr ""
"Tanda tanya - Menampilkan kotak dialog bantuan. Terkadang, aktifitas bisa "
"terlalu rumit untuk dijelaskan dengan mudah diarea deskripsi. Dalam hal ini, "
"fungsi ini memberi akses ke informasi tambahan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Tool box - Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
#| "repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris."
