"and select your language in the option of configuration."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; diinternasionalkan dan tersedia di lebih dari 50 bahasa. Jika "
"kamu ingin memeriksa apakah bahasamu tersedia, kamu bisa memulai &gcompris; "
"dan pilih bahasamu dipilihan konfigurasi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful, some languages need specific fonts to be displayed correctly."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If your language is not supported, you can contribute to the software and "
#| "add the translation of your language. If you are interested, you can "
#| "contact the <ulink url=\"http://l10n.kde.org/teams\">translation team</"
